What you need to know:  Uefa said an extraordinary meeting of its executive committee would be held on Friday at 1200 EAT and a decision is likely to be made on this season's Champions League finalThe showpiece game of European club football's premier competition is scheduled to be played on May 28 at the Gazprom Arena in Saint PetersburgEuropean football's governing body also has a major sponsorship deal with Gazprom, the Russian state energy giant